dinner in his honor at the presidential palace. Today (Juan 
Bautista Joffre), former Argentine ambassador to Panama, will 
host a luncheon for the Panamanian president. This evening 
Endara will attend a tango musical performance in the 
traditional San Telmo neighborhood. 
