<H3> <TI>   `Terrorists' Detonate Three Bombs, Damage Banks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Terrorists' Detonate Three Bombs, Damage Banks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA1806205294 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Canal 
A Network in Spanish 1800 GMT 18 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1806205294 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Canal 
A Network </F>

<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "NTC News" newscast] </F>
  [Text] A new wave of terror has been unleashed by 
terrorists who detonated three powerful bombs damaging three 
banks along the border. [not further specified] 
  The shock wave caused damage estimated at more than 100 
million pesos. The automatic tellers were destroyed, and a 
customer, who was seriously injured by the explosion, fights for 
his life. 
  No specific subversive group has claimed responsibility for 
the attack. 

</TEXT>

