<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by correspondent Jorge Brusco; from the "Union Radio </F>
News" newscast] 
  [Text] Bus owners have directly accused Governor Guillermo 
Cal of being responsible for the acts of violence that took 
place in Maturin and for the resulting damages to 25 buses. 
Representatives and leaders of the transportation sector and 5 
July Cooperative President Eudis Febres, 5 July Cooperative 
