<F P=102>   PA1806124094 Mexico City Radio ACIR Network in Spanish 0000 
GMT 18 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1806124094 </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City Radio ACIR Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


