Friendship Committee, referred to the peace agreements signed in 
Rome in 1992 with the opposition movement Renamo [Mozambique 
National Resistance] and the difficulties in fully implementing 
those agreements due to maneuvers by that armed organization. 
  Dos Santos is currently on a visit to Cuba which will end on 
30 June. During his stay he will meet with several leaders and 
will tour centers of economic, historical, scientific, 
educational, and social interest. 

