    [Editorial Report] Guayaquil EL UNIVERSO 0F 30 May 
announces that the results of a series of opinion polls 
conducted by Informe Confidencial will be published on page 1 of 
the newspaper, four times a week: Monday, Tuesday, Saturday, and 
Sunday. The polls will be conducted among residents of Guayaquil 
and Quito in an attempt to gather public opinion on various 
issues of national concern. 


